OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP quits party to
OL,4,Cjoin Reform UK
OL,6,FThe former Conservative MP for Bolton
OL,7,FWest has quit the party to join Reform
OL,8,FUK.
OL,10,FChris Green said he had been
OL,11,Fstruggling with the direction his
OL,12,Fparty was taking for more than a year,
OL,13,Fbut made his final decision after
OL,14,Flistening to Kemi Badenoch's
OL,15,Fleadership speech at the Conservative
OL,16,FParty Conference in October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
