OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP quits party to
OL,4,Cjoin Reform UK
OL,6,F"I wanted to give Kemi Badenoch the
OL,7,Fopportunity to keep me onside and she
OL,8,Fdidn't do it," he said, "You look at
OL,9,Fpolitics as it is, whether it's the
OL,10,FConservative Party, whether it's the
OL,11,FLabour Party, and they just aren't
OL,12,Feither saying the right things or
OL,13,Fthere is no belief that they'll
OL,14,Fdeliver on what they're saying. "
OL,16,F"And I listen to Reform, and I think
OL,17,Fthey've got the answers"
OL,19,FMr Green is one of three former
OL,20,FConservative MPs to quit in favour of
OL,21,FNigel Farage's party this week.
