OL,6,FHe served as the Tory representative
OL,7,Fin Bolton West for nine years, but
OL,8,Fsays he saw a disconnect in the party
OL,9,Fbetween what senior people said, and
OL,10,Fwhat they did.
OL,12,F"The obvious one on this is
OL,13,Fcontrolling migration, but also things
OL,14,Fsuch as levelling up and the Northern
OL,15,FPowerhouse. I never had the sense when
OL,16,FI was involved that they really had
OL,17,Fthat desire to deliver.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
