OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1764696188
OL,3,CFormer Conservative MP quits party to
OL,4,Cjoin Reform UK
OL,6,F"And it's that promise and then choice
OL,7,Fnot to deliver on that promise, which
OL,8,Fis a big reason why I've left the
OL,9,FConservative Party.... you can feel
OL,10,Fthe mood of the country, if the next
OL,11,FGeneral Election doesn't get a
OL,12,FGovernment that then starts delivering
OL,13,Ffor the country, you can just see
OL,14,Fpeople dispairing of democracy in
OL,15,Fgeneral"
OL,17,FThe former MP says reaction has been
OL,18,F"very mixed".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
