OL,6,F"Plenty of people are very supportive.
OL,7,FThe feedback on social media has been
OL,8,Fspectacular. Loads of people got in
OL,9,Ftouch to say "about time you did it!"
OL,10,FOther people obviously are
OL,11,Fdisappointed, having been a
OL,12,FConservative for a good number of
OL,13,Fyears, that I've left.
OL,15,F"But in general it's a very positive
OL,16,Freception and a huge amount of
OL,17,Fencouragement for me to get involved
OL,18,Fand support the Reform team."
