OL,6,FWhen asked if the defection was with a
OL,7,Fview to eventually running for
OL,8,Fparliament again, Mr Green said "I
OL,9,Fdon't know about that."
OL,11,F"It's a it's a long way off until I
OL,12,Fhave to make a decision either way.
OL,13,FAlso, I can't take for granted that
OL,14,Fthe Reform association locally will
OL,15,Fselect me. So it's a big process at
OL,16,Fthe moment - I'm focusing on
OL,17,Fsupporting the Reform team."
