OL,6,F"What I think is interesting is that
OL,7,Fthey choose to announce when the
OL,8,Fgovernment is on the ropes, the
OL,9,Fchancellor is in the dock. Reform are
OL,10,Fnot interested in what's happening to
OL,11,Fpeople out there, the money in their
OL,12,Fpockets, the cost of living. All
OL,13,Fthey're interested in is attacking
OL,14,FConservatives."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
