OL,4,Cjoin Reform UK
OL,6,FWhen asked about whether the
OL,7,FConservative defectors are merely
OL,8,Ftrying to further their own careers,
OL,9,FChris Green said "I can understand
OL,10,Fthat argument, but if anyone looks at
OL,11,Fhow I voted, the arguments I've made,
OL,12,Fhow I challenged the Conservative
OL,13,FParty and how I challenge Labour - I'm
OL,14,Fnot challenging from a left wing
OL,15,Fperspective, I'm challenging from more
OL,16,Fof a 'common ground perspective' that
OL,17,Fmany Reform voters would want me to do.
OL,19,F"So if you look at my values, you can
OL,20,Fsay this is a good fit."
